{"tid":2065770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美商務部允許美企與華為就5G標准進行合作","createTime":"2020-06-15T22:33:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T08:42:13.000Z","uid":141151,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"d8135f92ac270fae35096d0e08d2f9a582a225e4","tid":2065770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:33:50.000Z","msg":"美商務部允許美企與華為就5G標准進行合作<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/huawei-china-5g-ban-security-20200615/5463673.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fhuawei-china-5g-ban-security-20200615%2F5463673.html&d=UliE8fwpyfwMZiesMcCM7pB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=5bea924e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/huawei-china-5g-ban-security-20200615/5463673.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國商務部周一修改了禁止美國公司與中國電信巨頭華為開展業務的規定，允許雙方在就5G網絡標準制定方面進行合作。<br />\n<br />\n美國商務部長羅斯（Wilbur Ross）在聲明中說：&ldquo;商務部致力於通過鼓勵美國企業充分參與並倡導美國技術成為國際標準，來保護美國的國家安全和外交政策利益。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">根據新的規定，美國公司無需獲得商務部的許可證，即可在標準制定機構中與華為分享用於製定5G標準的相關信息。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n這項修改出台的一年前，美國以國家安全考慮為由，將華為列入商務部&ldquo;實體名單&rdquo;，禁止美國公司在未獲商務部許可證的情況下與美國公司進行任何業務往來。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">路透社援引行業官員說，在華為被列入商務部黑名單後，一些美國科技公司被迫停止與華為合作制定5G網絡標準，導致華為在一些標準制定上擁有更大話語權。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n全文請前往美國之音"},{"pid":"22901a2c2483f6ff77e700bc29fa4d0a98dba4a3","tid":2065770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:43:10.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e965bad2fd84e9079ebd842ae28c7df4a4845cc0","tid":2065770,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"22901a2c2483f6ff77e700bc29fa4d0a98dba4a3","tid":2065770,"uid":188176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:43:10.000Z","msg":"真定假<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:44:50.000Z","msg":"因為「一些美國科技公司被迫停止與華為合作制定5G網絡標準，導致華為在一些標準制定上擁有更大話語權」。"},{"pid":"4df2c1842c45dece02ae844791bcc2d62cde5616","tid":2065770,"uid":34816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T22:52:23.000Z","msg":"美國之音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468bb0358f19d2520277c754cc65c8cf686bbdad","tid":2065770,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:00:02.000Z","msg":"美國之音好似俾美國封殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce27e15746570e9bdf83761af7fb2f2f3234e15","tid":2065770,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:01:59.000Z","msg":"美國標準既5G"},{"pid":"448702affe541a7d2f5a3c1aeb6f8be868fe5dc1","tid":2065770,"uid":61520,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:07:49.000Z","msg":"check 下樓主post, 條友好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55d0759ba64542b031ff24f333c1151790a059db","tid":2065770,"uid":72795,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:08:43.000Z","msg":"連燈仔又燈中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1780ea53c56884b9315cdf147c80565b02939381","tid":2065770,"uid":296369,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-15T23:09:27.000Z","msg":"只係5G standards唔係佢d equipment......."},{"pid":"19106b5df7bfafa382cb9f3bb9da465c9ba95d57","tid":2065770,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote